'''伊朗王国大会'''（{{lang-fa|انجمن پادشاهی ایران|Anjoman-e Pâdeshâhi-ye Irân}}）又名'''閃雷'''（{{lang-fa|تندر}}），是總部设在[[洛杉矶|美国洛杉矶]]的[[伊朗|伊朗]]流亡反对派团体<ref>[http://www.timesonline.co.uk/tol/news/world/middle_east/article7007003.ece Iran hangs alleged dissidents to warn opposition] {{Wayback|url=http://www.timesonline.co.uk/tol/news/world/middle_east/article7007003.ece |date=20110604173715 }}, January 29, 2010</ref>，該團體主張推翻[[伊朗伊斯蘭共和國|伊朗伊斯蘭共和國]]，恢復[[巴列维王朝|巴列维王朝]]统治<ref name="jamestown">[http://www.jamestown.org/single/?no_cache=1&tx_ttnews%5Btt_news%5D=4936 Iranian Monarchist Group Claims Responsibility for Shiraz Mosque Attack] {{Wayback|url=http://www.jamestown.org/single/?no_cache=1&tx_ttnews%5Btt_news%5D=4936 |date=20160303195156 }}, ''Terrorism Focus'', Volume: 5 Issue: 20, May 20, 2008</ref>。该團體目前在[[伊朗|伊朗伊斯兰共和国]]屬於非法組織，不過在美国不屬於[[恐怖组织|恐怖组织]]<ref name="ynet">Yitzhak Benhorin. [http://www.ynetnews.com/articles/0,7340,L-3887524,00.html Iran: LA Terror group working against us] {{Wayback|url=http://www.ynetnews.com/articles/0,7340,L-3887524,00.html |date=20181025111713 }}.</ref>。 

